data.description: No city tax! Here's your opportunity to call Powell home. Located just off Clinton Hwy. 1700 square feet, 3 bed 2 bath. Fenced in and level back yard with 2 outbuildings. Bring the rocking chair for the front porch. Bring the couch for the screened in back porch. Newer flooring installed throughout the home. Spacious garage. Plenty of storage options. Come on home!
